title: Episode 12 - Cody Ko and Noel Miller
description:
Tiny Meat Gang joins the pod to talk about life all the way back in 2019. Cody and Noel discuss the differences between their world and Josh's. A quick round of Zoomer vs Boomer, and as always, the weeks latest Sway House drama.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/bffspod
